<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Booking Confirmation</title>
    <style>
        /* Reset CSS */
        body, h1, h2, p {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: #333;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center; /* Center horizontally */
            align-items: center; /* Center vertically */
            height: 100vh; /* Full viewport height */
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #007bff;
        }

        p {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .booking-details {
            border-top: 2px solid #007bff;
            padding-top: 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .booking-details h2 {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: #007bff;
        }

        .highlight {
            color: #007bff;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .booking-details p {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .button:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }

        @media screen and (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                width: 90%;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
   
    <div class="container">
        <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 20px;">
            <img src="https://lynklegal.com/assets/lynkLogo-BTwXxail.png" alt="Lynk Legal Logo" style="max-width: 330px; width: 100%; height: auto;">
        </div>
        <h1>Booking Genration</h1>
        <p>Dear <%= user_name %></p>
        <p>Your booking has been confirmed successfully. Below are the details of your booking:</p>
        <div class="booking-details">
            <h2>Booking Details:</h2>
            <p><strong>Booking ID:</strong> <%= bookingID %></p>
            <p><strong>Expert:</strong> <%= expert_name %></p>
            <p><strong>Service:</strong> <%= service_name %></p>
            <p><strong>Expert Fees:</strong> <%= find_service_cost %></p>
        </div>
        <p><strong>We will notify you once when the booking got accepted by <span class="highlight"><%= expert_name %></span></strong></p>
        <p>If you have any questions or need further assistance, please feel free to contact us.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
